title: Sora no Otoshimono: Forte (Heaven's Lost Property: Forte)
synopsis: Sakurai Tomoki has settled into his life with the two angeloids, Ikaros and Nymph, and is enjoying himself immensely.  However, he keeps having weird dreams and asks all of his friends to help him investigate the cause.
